Bruno Bonfils wrote:
> PS : i'm looking for the way to do a periodic rehash.. it's possible ?

would you believe
  periodic() { rehash; }
?  You need to pick a period in seconds.
  PERIOD=60

It will only run before a prompt, but that's when you need it.

